Purpose: Sends an HTTP Put Request to GitHub to upload the full event archive of a soc case for investigation and helpful aid.
Node Type: Http Node

Setup:
  Name: GitHub_Cyber_Event_Archive
  Action: PUT
  URL: https://api.github.com/repos/CS4850-ASMCyberProject/cyber_event_archive/contents/$get_ts.message.path
  Body: {"message":"$get_ts.message.commit_msg","content":"$get_ts.message.github_event","branch":"main"}
  Headers: Authorization: Bearer YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN
           Accept: application/vnd.github+json
           Content-Type: application/json

Workflow Path:
  12_Get_TS -> 13_GitHub_Cyber_Event_Archive -> 14_Get_TS_Copy (No Conditional Branching)
